Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-tablelog
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, postgresql-PGVERSION
Description: log changes on tables and restore tables to point in time
 PostgreSQL Table Log uses a trigger to log any INSERTs, UPDATEs and DELETEs on
 a specific table into another table. The second part of tablelog is able to
 restore the state of the original table or of a specific row for any time in
 the past.
